  "body_html": "<h3 id=\"rdPHY\"><span>多步骤试验的计数法则</span></h3><p>如果一个试验可以分为循序的 k 个步骤，在第 1 步中有 N1 种试验结果，在第 2 步中有 N2 种试验结果...以此类推。那么所有的试验结果的总数为 N1*N2*N3...*Nk。</p><blockquote><p>举例：抛 3 次硬币，每次都有正反两种结果。所以试验结果的总数是 2X2<span>X2</span>=8 种。</p></blockquote><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"AIK0J\"><span>组合计数法则</span></h3><p>从N项中任取n项的组合数</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/9d2501f94cb082365102df0c254d88e7.svg#card=math&amp;code=C_%7Bn%7D%5E%7BN%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7BN%20%21%7D%7Bn%20%21%28N-n%29%20%21%7D&amp;height=45&amp;width=134\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 134px;\" /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #8C8C8C;\">*N和n的上下位置与我们平常见的是相反的，因为我们这里是以欧美规范为主。</span></p><p><br /></p><blockquote><p>举例子：从5个彩色球中，选出2个彩球，有多少种选法？</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/a5262445c96ff5cca8f950e54b47c8b4.svg#card=math&amp;code=C_%7B2%7D%5E%7B5%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B5%20%21%7D%7B2%20%21%285-2%29%20%21%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B5%20%5Ctimes%204%20%5Ctimes%203%20%5Ctimes%202%20%5Ctimes%201%7D%7B%282%20%5Ctimes%201%29%20%5Ctimes%283%20%5Ctimes%202%20%5Ctimes%201%29%7D%3D10&amp;height=45&amp;width=341\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 341px;\" /></p></blockquote><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"Wckk9\"><span>排列计数法则</span></h3><p>从N项中任取n项的排列数</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/fada666178e35eda87fad4163dc7d4f7.svg#card=math&amp;code=P_%7Bn%7D%5E%7BN%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7BN%20%21%7D%7B%28N-n%29%20%21%7D&amp;height=45&amp;width=119\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 119px;\" /></p><blockquote><p>举例子：从5个彩色球中，选出2个彩球，有多少种排列方法？</p><p>代入得出答案是20种</p></blockquote><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><hr /><p>参考文献：</p><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTI3MzUwMA==&amp;mid=2650016011&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=29e571f0b0bfedff6d418903b9e64107&amp;chksm=beb8ae7889cf276ecadc945c0b6ff074d60644a11c68c4aba44ceb8e12010d3c0b9829729183#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTI3MzUwMA==&amp;mid=2650016011&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=29e571f0b0bfedff6d418903b9e64107&amp;chksm=beb8ae7889cf276ecadc945c0b6ff074d60644a11c68c4aba44ceb8e12010d3c0b9829729183#wechat_redirect</a></p>",
